  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this randomized double-blind cross over clinical trial is to investigate
      effectiveness of different routes of applications (intramuscular and submucous at the site of
      surgery) and doses (4 mg and 8 mg) of Dexamethasone on swelling, trismus, pain and quality of
      life after lower third molar surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
