  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy patients (ASA I)

          -  Bilateral symmetrically impacted lower third molars according to Pel-Gregory's and
             Winter's classification

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Heavy tobacco smokers

          -  Drug and / or alcohol abusers
      </textblock>
